{"tid":2384201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「尿袋」起火爆炸印傭燒傷　延醫6日不治","createTime":"2021-01-28T11:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T12:17:43.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b021be2709cb076ace98bc3e98b4849a00791f7c","tid":2384201,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:49:16.000Z","msg":"青衣長安邨於上周四(21日)下午發生火警，一名36歲印傭在火警中身體多處燒傷，送往瑪嘉烈醫院救治，惜於延醫6日後，於昨午(27日)1時許證實不治。其姓胡(87歲)女僱主當日亦曾被困火場，吸入濃煙不適需送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日安江樓一個單位突然起火，更一度傳出爆炸聲。消防及後調查火警起因，<span class=\"red\">相信事發時死者正在用一個俗稱「尿袋」的外置充電器為其電話充電，惟尿袋突然爆炸。死者走避不及被燒着上衣</span>，火勢迅速蔓延封鎖大門，死者及年邁僱主一度被困單位內需由消防救出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nX國製造？"},{"pid":"9fa1cf8102efc7fc0e70f4cb9fb2a1e65ba015ec","tid":2384201,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"九成九尿袋都係支那造"},{"pid":"e3edb2415add083574e8c27952fc9abe790fc046","tid":2384201,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:57:02.000Z","msg":"成龍：.............."},{"pid":"bc20ca8d3ebdf1da66f28070870c33fc205b531e","tid":2384201,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"喺屋入面做乜鳩用尿袋叉電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db7763fe130d6a1f187a40e3caf3a51c68a8122","tid":2384201,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc20ca8d3ebdf1da66f28070870c33fc205b531e","tid":2384201,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"喺屋入面做乜鳩用尿袋叉電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"想一路叉一路玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c357ae3848d579c7f7ded332ee8d908e095983","tid":2384201,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"客死異鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/an